&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Liaison &amp;amp; MSP Coordination&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Act as on-site point of contact for the Managed Service Provider, triaging tickets, managing escalations, monitoring SLAs, and coordinating issue resolution across users, MSP, and internal teams. Build strong relationships with support and engineering teams to improve responsiveness and service quality.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Security Support&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Support vulnerability remediation efforts including patching, configuration hardening, and tracking across endpoints. Assist with incident response activities and maintain security hygiene including MFA, certificate management, and access reviews.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Infrastructure &amp;amp; Projects&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
